title: Dell Mini 9 Ubuntu Netbook Remix - Restore iso image
description:
***This iso will ONLY work on a Dell Mini 9 netbook***

Bought your Dell Mini 9with XP Home and wish that you had gotten Linux instead? Well just burn this iso to a DVD. Then plug in an External USB DVD-ROM and boot this restore image to get Linux on your Mini 9.

Much thanks to UnaClocker from the MyDellMini.com forum. http://www.mydellmini.com/forum/index.php

Enjoy!
